 results show that the gravitational collapse of the\ncondensed dark matter halos can lead to the formation of stable astrophysical\nsystems with both galactic and stellar sizes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Mar 2014 18:36:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Apr 2014 07:50:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
